{"tid":1775991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工展會明開幕將實施入場安全檢查不准帶政治色彩宣傳品","createTime":"2019-12-09T08:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T12:58:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cc0aa7092ba32d71e3038f29ebb23836beedeb3f","tid":1775991,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:12:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496737-20191209.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496737-20191209.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=49a49e85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496737-20191209.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cc54dfcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496737-20191209.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n工展會明日開幕，共設700個攤位。展期至本月31號，為期22日，較往年短，每日展覽時間亦提前至晚上8時結束。<br />\n<br />\n廠商會第二副會長徐晉暉說，在現時社會環境下舉辦大型活動甚有挑戰，但廠商會將確保工展會有序進行。今屆工展會將實施「入場安全檢查」，市民不得帶攻擊性或危險品、具政治色彩宣傳品、非飲用液體等入場。<br />\n<br />\n徐晉暉說，考慮到社會事件及中美貿易戰打擊本港各行各業，廠商會減免工展會參展商3成租金，亦減低入場門票價格至8元。大會亦推出多項購物優惠，刺激市民消費。"},{"pid":"2efeaf7e678ffbeca449a35b557b4557ce0d5b75","tid":1775991,"uid":170812,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:14:46.000Z","msg":"逐個搜袋，師奶聽到都覺得煩唔想去"},{"pid":"b0d8a29bc514343ca4f8c35f2e60002b4a3db8e1","tid":1775991,"uid":193642,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:17:09.000Z","msg":"俾8蚊入場幫人清貨"},{"pid":"cd3c187c07fafe393f6eee80180ca89fff9515ff","tid":1775991,"uid":306621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"係佢地門口搞活動<br />\n我最鐘意睇人去工展會買野"},{"pid":"c229fc6a411e7d1aec72b45b4b59c84870a6e2db","tid":1775991,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p